								<wikidot:authorUserId>3146689</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p><em>He just wants a simple life</em>. Sweet article, some of those journal lines really hit close to home.</p> <p>I do think this &quot;thank you, Foundation&quot; at the end is a slight misstep because it takes the focus away from the main message (the farm, that is) and I don't dig the cruel Foundation in this context. I love the idea and overall narrative though, so I've upvoted.</p> 
				 	]]>
